 {
  "text": "Hi, I am Mark. Let me tell you about the food I like. I love coffee. I drink three cups every day. For lunch, I like chicken with rice. It is my favorite meal. I also like fish, but only on weekends. I eat a lot of fruit because it is healthy. I eat an apple every morning. I do not like salad very much, but my wife loves it. And I drink a lot of water during the day. Good food makes me happy.",
  "voice": "arthur",
  "file": "a5_listening_mark_food.mp3"
 },
 {
  "text": "Hello, my name is Anna. I want to tell you about my favorite food. In the morning, I eat bread with fruit, and I drink coffee. I like a big breakfast. For lunch, I usually eat fish with a green salad. I really like fresh salad. I do not like chicken, so I never order it. When I go to a restaurant, I always ask for water. My favorite restaurant is near my house. The food there is delicious. I am very happy when I eat good food.",
  "voice": "ellen",
  "file": "a5_listening_anna_food.mp3"
 },
 {
